{"id":250144,"link":"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/2012/09/维权网-黑龙江棚户区居民遭断水逼迁，提起行政/","date":"2012-09-04T05:31:01Z","modified":"2012-09-04T05:31:01Z","title":"维权网 | 黑龙江棚户区居民遭断水逼迁，提起行政诉讼法院不立案（图）","content":"<p><div dir=\"ltr\"></p>\n<div></div>\n<p><a rel=\"nofollow\" name='more'></a></p>\n<div><span>（维权网信息员李军报道）黑龙江省鸡西市鸡冠区幸福里棚户区改造项目为了把拆迁进行下去，对棚户区断水、断路，严重干扰了居民正常的生活。截止</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">9</span><span>月</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">3</span><span>日</span><span>，棚户区被断水</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">22</span><span>日。棚户区居民赖以生存的自来水管道设施被埋，居民们自己在废墟里面寻找水源。刚刚学会走步的宝宝，学会的第一项业务就是排队接水，居民们看着饥渴的宝宝，不禁愤怒发问，你们还是人吗？</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></div>\n<div></div>\n<div><span>棚户区居民曾经要求见朱得义市长，被拒绝。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">8</span><span>月</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">25</span><span>日</span><span>，棚户区的居民刘霞向黑龙江省鸡西市城市管理行政执法局邮寄了一封信息公开申请的挂号信，</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">8</span><span>月</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">28</span><span>日</span><span>，刘霞接到被执法局拒绝接收被返回的邮件。这个鸡冠区幸福里棚户区改造项目没有任何审批手续，执法局却视而不见。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></div>\n<div></div>\n<div><span lang=\"EN-US\">9</span><span>月</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">2</span><span>日</span><span>凌晨</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">2</span><span>点，一户被遭受逼迁人家的玻璃，被不明身份人砸碎，报警多次警察才于早</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">7</span><span>点钟出警。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></div>\n<div></div>\n<div><span lang=\"EN-US\">8</span><span>月</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">22</span><span>日</span><span>，棚户区居民对鸡西市政府征收办公室提起行政诉讼，将行政诉讼状提交到鸡西市中级法院。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">9</span><span>月</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">3</span><span>日</span><span>，单亚娟等多位棚户区居民到鸡西市中级法院见到刘法官，质询按照《行政诉讼法》第四十二条的规定，法院在接到起诉状后</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">7</span><span>日内立案，要么依法给一个不予受理的裁定。但是刘法官表示不能立案，也不能给出不予受理的裁定，自己无权作这个决定，要服从鸡西的大局。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></div>\n<div><span><br /></span></div>\n<div><a rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://2.bp.blogspot.com/-hu-O6SKB2vc/UEWCVRNV-0I/AAAAAAAANDo/EeZHDxpxRos/s1600/%E6%88%AA%E5%9B%BE00.jpg\"><img border=\"0\" height=\"317\" src=\"http://2.bp.blogspot.com/-hu-O6SKB2vc/UEWCVRNV-0I/AAAAAAAANDo/EeZHDxpxRos/s320/%E6%88%AA%E5%9B%BE00.jpg\" width=\"320\" /></a></div>\n<p></p>\n<div><a rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://4.bp.blogspot.com/-FInIY3FrZa0/UEWCXxllleI/AAAAAAAANDw/sYPCZbxdAjM/s1600/5.jpg\"><img border=\"0\" height=\"207\" src=\"http://4.bp.blogspot.com/-FInIY3FrZa0/UEWCXxllleI/AAAAAAAANDw/sYPCZbxdAjM/s320/5.jpg\" width=\"320\" /></a></div>\n<div><span><br /></span></div>\n<div></div>\n<div><span>相关参见：</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"><a rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://wqw2010.blogspot.com/2012/08/blog-post_9286.html\">http://wqw2010.blogspot.com/2012/08/blog-post_9286.html</a></span></div>\n</div>\n<div><img width=\"1\" height=\"1\" src=\"https://blogger.googleusercontent.com/tracker/751033951089627103-4344643729325986324?l=wqw2010.blogspot.com\" alt=\"\" /></div>\n</p>\n<p><small>本文由自动聚合程序取自网络，内容和观点不代表数字时代立场</small></p>\n<form method=\"POST\" action=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.us4.list-manage.com/subscribe/post?u=17daa75df533f6c6ff72e51ab&#038;id=2ea93c5b7b\">\n<a href=\"http://eepurl.com/msuvD\">墙外新闻实时更新 欢迎订阅数字时代</a><br />\n <br /><input type=\"email\" value=\"\" name=\"EMAIL\" id=\"mce-EMAIL_in_post\" size=\"25\" style=\"display:block;\" placeholder=\"请输入您的邮件地址\" required><br />\n\t<input type=\"submit\" value=\"点击订阅\" name=\"subscribe\" style=\"height: 20px;\" id=\"in_post_subscribe\"><br />\n</form>\n","author":997,"categories":[18269,20534],"tags":[19196]}